sequenceDiagram
    actor Buyer
    participant Frontend as React Frontend
    participant Backend as Node.js Backend
    participant DB as PostgreSQL (PostGIS)
    participant S3 as Amazon S3

    %% Browsing and Spatial Search
    Buyer->>Frontend: Search for properties (map area/filters)
    Frontend->>Backend: GET /api/properties
    Backend->>DB: Query data
    DB-->>Backend: Return matching real estate listings (with S3 URLs)
    Backend-->>Frontend: JSON property list
    
    %% Direct S3 Asset Retrieval
    Frontend->>S3: GET /bucket/property-images/... (Fetch media)
    S3-->>Frontend: Return image files
    Frontend-->>Buyer: Display properties with loaded images on map/UI